  "body": "## üéâ Description\r\n\r\nThe new nonReentrant function uses a local variable which counts toward the stack limit for any functions that use this modifier, making some contracts unable to be compiled.\r\n\r\nResults in the error: `CompilerError: Stack too deep, try removing local variables.`\r\n\r\n- [ ] üêõ This is a bug report.\r\n- [x] üìà This is a feature request.\r\n\r\n<!-- Please check one of the above by placing an x in the box. -->\r\n\r\n## üíª Environment\r\n\r\nThis is a change from v1.11 to v1.12\r\n",
